Powered by Intel's latest Core M3-8100Y Processor

And because your Surface Go 2 has two cameras, which are both Full HD, you can easily catch up with friends and family without losing out on video quality.For the whole familyWith its parent-managed screen time limits, spending control and content filtering features, you can make the Surface Go 2 a tablet for the whole family. Choose the version with 128 GB of SSD storage to save all those precious family photos and videos that you can treasure for years to come.
